         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 8 September 1873 ¶  ¶ I am writing only a few words with this mail, esteemed friend, to thank you for the kind naming and return of the algae, ¶  also for the valuable publications. ¶  ¶ I...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">73.09.08c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. <seg style="">Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">8/9/73</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich schreibe nur wenige Worte mit dieser Post, verrehrter Freund, um Ihnen für die gütige Benennung u. Rücksendung der Algen to danken, auch für die werthvollen Schriften. Ich habe in einer neuen Abhandlung über Tasmaniens Pflanzen die Algen unter Ihrer dortigen Königl. Gesellschaft vorgeschlagen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Liste der Chatham Insel Algen ist an das philos. Institut von Neu-Seeland gesandt.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit ehrender Ergebenheit</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Hoffentlich ist Lieut. Blomstedt mit der Alsophilen glücklich angekommen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich bitte ja Ihre edle Zeit nicht mit blossen Benennen </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">meinet</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">wegen zu verbringen, sondern nur nach eignen Studien zum Gewinn der Wissenschaft zu trachten. Beruhigen</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Beunruhigen?</p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> Sie sich nicht um Zurücksendungen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Könnte Ihre Meisterhan uns nicht einen </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">einfachen Index</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> mit Synonymen der Algen der Erde liefern.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">8 September 1873</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am writing only a few words with this mail, esteemed friend, to thank you for the kind naming and return of the algae,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Duplicates of the Chatham Island algae collected by Henry Traves during spring/summer 1871-2, sent by M to J. Agardh by <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Sommersetshire</seg> in August 1872. See M to J. Agardh, 28 August 1872. See also M to J. Agardh, 23 April 1873.</p>
               </note> also for the valuable publications.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In a new paper on Tasmania's plants I have included the algae under your authority<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Agardh's list of algae is included in B74.13.05.</p>
               </note> and also proposed you as honorary member of the Royal Society there.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Agardh was elected a corresponding member at the Society's September 1873 meeting; see <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Papers and proceedings of the Royal Society of Tasmania for 1873</seg>, p. 49.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The list of the Chatham Island algae has been sent to the Philosophical Institute of New Zealand.<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Incorporated within B74.06.01.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With respectful devotion</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I hope that Lieutenant Blomstedt<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to J. Agardh, 23 April 1873.</p>
               </note> has arrived safely with the <name key="Alsophila">Alsophila</name>s.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Please do not spend your precious time purely with naming algae <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">on my account</hi>
               </seg>, but aim only at your own studies for the benefit of science. Do not be worried about the returning of specimens.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Could not your master's hand furnish us with a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">simple index</hi>
               </seg> with synonyms of the algae of the world?</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Alsophila">Alsophila</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
